    (9,'self_reported','This information is entered by either the principal or another school representative from each school.','2012-07-13 17:41:35','2013-09-18 03:48:33','Self-Reported Information'),
    (10,'other_details','<p>Acknowledges challenges faced by schools that serve higher populations of low-income students, English language learners and special education students.  High schools can also earn credit for high FAFSA completion rates. Included for all schools.</p>','2012-07-13 17:41:35','2013-09-18 01:24:38','Extra Credit'),
