    (24,'climate_site_s','<p>The Community Review measures the feedback given by members of the Detroit community who visited the school. Excellent Schools Detroit conducts unannounced community site reviews to schools as part of the annual school review process. Community reviewers receive extensive training and orientation and are led on the visits by trained team leaders. At the conclusion of each visit, the community reviewers assess the school by completing a survey; a final score is calculated based on the survey.</p>\r\n<p>The survey asks community reviewers to assess three categories of the school climate: safe and caring environment, high expectations for learning and parent and community partnerships, using a Likert scale that ranges from strongly agree to strongly disagree. Schools with more strongly agree selections have higher site visit scores.</p>\r\n  <TABLE>\r\n   <TBODY>\r\n     <TR>\r\n        <TD>\r\n          Site Visit Average\r\n        </TD>\r\n     </TR>\r\n   </TBODY>\r\n    <TBODY>\r\n     <TR>\r\n        <TD>\r\n          <BR>\r\n          \r\n        </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          Floor\r\n       </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          1.5\r\n       </TD>\r\n     </TR>\r\n   </TBODY>\r\n    <TBODY>\r\n     <TR>\r\n        <TD>\r\n          <BR>\r\n          \r\n        </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          Target\r\n        </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          3.75\r\n        </TD>\r\n     </TR>\r\n   </TBODY>\r\n    <TBODY>\r\n     <TR>\r\n        <TD>\r\n          Points\r\n        </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          Min\r\n       </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          Max\r\n       </TD>\r\n     </TR>\r\n     <TR>\r\n        <TD>\r\n          0\r\n       </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          <BR>\r\n          \r\n        </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          <BR>\r\n          \r\n        </TD>\r\n     </TR>\r\n     <TR>\r\n        <TD>\r\n          1\r\n       </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          <BR>\r\n          \r\n        </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          <B