    (26,'climate_five_e_grwth','<p>The 5Essentials Net score is a measure of a school’s 2013 5Essentials survey. The 5Essential Growth score is a measure of a schools growth or lack of growth from the 2012 to 2013 survey. The 5 Essentials framework was created and validated by the University of Chicago Consortium on School Research. <A CLASS=\"sdfootnoteanc\" NAME=\"sdfootnote1anc\" HREF=\"#sdfootnote1sym\"><SUP>1</SUP></A></p>\r\n<TABLE>\r\n    <TBODY>\r\n     <TR>\r\n        <TD>\r\n          Five E Growth\r\n       </TD>\r\n     </TR>\r\n   </TBODY>\r\n    <TBODY>\r\n     <TR>\r\n        <TD>\r\n          <BR>\r\n          \r\n        </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          Floor\r\n       </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          -5\r\n        </TD>\r\n     </TR>\r\n   </TBODY>\r\n    <TBODY>\r\n     <TR>\r\n        <TD>\r\n          <BR>\r\n          \r\n        </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          Target\r\n        </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          3\r\n       </TD>\r\n     </TR>\r\n   </TBODY>\r\n    <TBODY>\r\n     <TR>\r\n        <TD>\r\n          Points\r\n        </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          Min\r\n       </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          Max\r\n       </TD>\r\n     </TR>\r\n     <TR>\r\n        <TD>\r\n          0\r\n       </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          <BR>\r\n          \r\n        </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          <BR>\r\n          \r\n        </TD>\r\n     </TR>\r\n     <TR>\r\n        <TD>\r\n          1\r\n       </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          -4\r\n        </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          -3\r\n        </TD>\r\n     </TR>\r\n     <TR>\r\n        <TD>\r\n          2\r\n       </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          -2\r\n        </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          -2\r\n        </TD>\r\n     </TR>\r\n     <TR>\r\n        <TD>\r\n          3\r\n       </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          -1\r\n        </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          0\r\n       </TD>\r\n     </TR>\r\n     <TR>\r\n        <TD>\r\n          4\r\n       </TD>\r\n       <TD>\r\n          1\r\n       